<h2>Alain Robbe-Grillet - Szenarien der Schaulust (Sammelband)</h2>
<h3></h3>
<hr>
<abbr class='unapi-id' title='822'></abbr>
<div class='row-fluid'>
<div class='span8'>
<h3>Allgemeine Angaben</h3>
